<section class="L1" id="about">
  <div id="headline">
    <h3>I Build Products & Brands</h3>
    <p>At Boundary I designed the first version of our web product and have led product design to over 100 paying customers. At TankH2O I helped create both a product and a brand that connect deeply with customers, selling in more than 50 stores in under a year. My 10+ years of product experience span the physical and the digital worlds, and I've built products and teams from the ground up.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="container-fluid">
